title: Futbol Americas: Orlando City wins U.S. Open Cup
description:
On Wednesday’s episode of Futbol Americas, Sebastian Salazar and Herculez Gomez live from Orlando City’s Exploria Stadium, react to the U.S. Open Cup final between Orlando City and Sacramento Republic. Does Orlando City's title win have an asterisk? Then the guys talk about the news of Chelsea sacking head coach Thomas Tuchel. What does this mean for Christian Pulisic?
